      <div class="footer-col footer-brand">
        <a href="/" class="logo">roha<span class="dot">.</span></a>
        <p class="tagline">A quiet kind of warm.</p>
        <p>A small studio in Sumatra. We build websites, UI/UX, and brands for founders and indie makers who want to ship something that feels real.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="footer-col">
        <h4>Pages</h4>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
          <li><a href="/work">Work</a></li>
          <li><a href="/services">Services</a></li>
          <li><a href="/shop">Shop</a></li>
          <li><a href="/about">About</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="footer-col">
        <h4>Services</h4>
